list.t:
iCalendar
specifies a core specification of objects, data types,
properties and property parameters;

section.t:
This specification registers a well-known URI for the DKIM HTTP-based public key management information, "domainkey" (see ). To retrieve information about the public key used to sign an iSchedule message, the iSchedule Sender constructs a URI of the form:
https://{srv-host}:{srv-port}/.well-known/domainkey/{d}/{s}
; {srv-host} is the host name from the _domainkey_lookup SRV record ; {srv-port} is the port number from the _domainkey_lookup SRV record ; {d} is the d= value from the "DKIM-Signature" header. ; {s} is the s= value from the "DKIM-Signature" header.
